id="gentle-wave" d="M-160 44c30 0 58-18 88-18s 58 18 88 18 58-18 88-18 58 18 88 18 v44h-352z"/></defs><g class="parallax"><use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="0"/><use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="3"/><use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="5"/><use xlink:href="#gentle-wave" x="48" y="7"/></g></svg></div><main><div class="inner"><div id="main" class="pjax"><div class="article wrap"><div class="breadcrumb" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList"><i class="ic i-home"></i> <span><a href="/">首页</a></span><i class="ic i-angle-right"></i> <span class="current" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem"><a href="/categories/java/" itemprop="item" rel="index" title="分类于 Java"><span itemprop="name">Java</span></a><meta itemprop="position" content="1"></span></div><article itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article" class="post block" lang="zh-CN"><link itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" href="https://www.baiyezi.vip/shiro%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8"><span hidden itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><meta itemprop="image" content="/images/avatar.png"><meta itemprop="name" content="fanfanfan"><meta itemprop="description" content=", 花有重开日，人无再少年"></span><span hidden itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization"><meta itemprop="name" content="书院十四先生"></span><div class="body md" itemprop="articleBody"><h2 id="shiro介绍"><a class="anchor" href="#shiro介绍">#</a> shiro 介绍</h2><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL3NoaXJvLmFwYWNoZS5vcmcv">shiro 官网</span></p><p><strong>Apache Shiro™</strong> is a powerful and easy-to-use Java security framework that performs authentication, authorization, cryptography, and session management. With Shiro’s easy-to-understand API, you can quickly and easily secure any application – from the smallest mobile applications to the largest web and enterprise applications.</p><p>大致意思就是，shiro 是一个简单易用的 java 安全框架，提供功能有认证、授权、加密以及 session 管理等，通过 shiro 一些简单的 API，可以快速将 shiro 应用于移动应用、大型万张以及企业级应用。</p><h2 id="shiro组件"><a class="anchor" href="#shiro组件">#</a> shiro 组件</h2><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucHJvY2Vzc29uLmNvbS92aWV3L2xpbmsvNjAzZjNmZDgwNzkxMjk1MWZmMmQ5NGRk">shiro 知识点导图在线查看</span></p><ul><li>Authentication：用户登录认证<ul><li>Subject：请求登录的任何个体，如用户</li><li>Realm：用户与 shiro 之间的桥梁，当有多种登录方式（账号密码、手机号验证码、第三方登录）时就会有多个 Realm</li></ul></li><li>Authorization：角色授权</li><li>Session：用户会话的管理</li><li>Cryptography：加密处理</li><li>Caching：用户信息缓存</li><li>Remember Me：记住我功能</li><li>Testing：测试支持</li><li>Web：web 支持</li><li>Concurrency：支持多线程并发验证，能在线程创建的时候传播下去，即 session 信息能在多线程代码中获取的到</li></ul><p><img data-src="shiro%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8.assets/image-20210303105533889.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="shiro请求流程"><a class="anchor" href="#shiro请求流程">#</a> shiro 请求流程</h2><p><img data-src="shiro%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8.assets/image-20210303160055592.png" alt=""></p><p><img data-src="shiro%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8.assets/image-20210303110949528.png" alt=""></p><h2 id="简单测试"><a class="anchor" href="#简单测试">#</a> 简单测试</h2><p>新建一个 maven 项目，导入相关依赖</p><figure class="highlight xml"><figcaption data-lang="XML"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre><span class="token prolog">&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>project</span> <span class="token attr-name">xmlns</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre>         <span class="token attr-name"><span class="token namespace">xmlns:</span>xsi</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class="token punctuation">"</spa