ealms"><span class="toc-number">5.</span> <span class="toc-text">Realms</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#authorizingrealm"><span class="toc-number">5.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">AuthorizingRealm</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8A%A0%E5%AF%86"><span class="toc-number">6.</span> <span class="toc-text">加密</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8"><span class="toc-number">7.</span> <span class="toc-text">异常</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83"><span class="toc-number">8.</span> <span class="toc-text">授权</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F"><span class="toc-number">8.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">授权方式</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div><div class="related panel pjax" data-title="系列文章"><ul><li><a href="/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85MySQL" rel="bookmark" title="Linux下安装MySQL">Linux下安装MySQL</a></li><li><a href="/MySQL%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80" rel="bookmark" title="MySQL基础">MySQL基础</a></li><li><a href="/IOC%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89" rel="bookmark" title="IOC配置方式（一）">IOC配置方式（一）</a></li><li><a href="/IOC%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89" rel="bookmark" title="IOC配置方式（二）">IOC配置方式（二）</a></li><li><a href="/IOC%E6%B3%A8%E8%A7%A3%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F" rel="bookmark" title="IOC注解方式">IOC注解方式</a></li><li><a href="/AOP" rel="bookmark" title="AOP">AOP</a></li><li><a href="/SpringBoot%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8" rel="bookmark" title="SpringBoot入门">SpringBoot入门</a></li><li><a href="/SpringBoot-Web%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91" rel="bookmark" title="SpringBoot-Web开发">SpringBoot-Web开发</a></li><li><a href="/SpringBoot%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86" rel="bookmark" title="SpringBoot自动装配原理">SpringBoot自动装配原理